data.description: Beautiful Cape Cod home at the Elizabethtown Country Club. This home features a covered front porch and large deck off of the kitchen. The exterior also features nice landscaping and also a detached building (18x24 with electric) that can be used as a workshop, storage or place to put your golf cart. The interior features a main level family room with a fireplace, living room, formal dining room and kitchen with appliances and a breakfast bar, half bath and utility room. The upstairs features and master bedroom and bathroom, a second and third bedroom and another full bath. This home is ready to move into. The home has had updates recently. New HVAC 2019, roof 2021, sump pump and dehumidifier in crawl space in 2020 and new garage doors and openers. This property has a VA assumable loan
